Package: Rflow
Title: Professional AI Assistant for RStudio
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Carly", "Chery", email = "cchery@earth.ac.cr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An advanced AI coding assistant that lives inside RStudio.
    Get expert help with R programming, data analysis, visualization, and
    statistical modeling through a clean, professional chat interface. Powered
    by Claude Sonnet 4.5 with 1730+ expert training prompts and direct access
    to R 4.5.2 source code for deep understanding. Features include: AI-powered
    analysis, publication-level plots, direct R integration, real-time streaming,
    smart data loading, and automatic error recovery.
